Kwamamaza cyangwa [https://samarketingdigital.com.br/ marketing], gucuruza cyangwa, gake cyane, gucuruza,  nubuhanga bwo gushakisha, guhanga no gutanga agaciro kugirango uhaze ibikenewe na / cyangwa ibyifuzo byisoko ryabaguzi. Ibicuruzwa, serivisi cyangwa ibitekerezo bishobora gushimisha abakoresha birakoreshwa. Kubwibyo birakenewe gushiraho ingamba zisobanutse zizakoreshwa mugurisha, itumanaho no mugutezimbere ubucuruzi. Intego yo kwamamaza ni ugushiraho agaciro no gukurura abakiriya, gushiraho umubano wunguka kumpande zombi. Ibikorwa byumuyobozi ushinzwe kwamamaza bikubiyemo ibikorwa byinshi, uhereye kubushakashatsi bwisoko, gusobanura ingamba zo guhitamo isoko,  kwamamaza, kwamamaza no kugurisha. Nko mu micungire yimikoranire yabakiriya, nigice kinini cyingenzi muri sosiyete iyo ariyo yose kandi gisaba uburyo nubuhanga bunoze.

Byongeye kandi, abashobora kuba abakiriya nabo ni ahantu ho kwigwa hagomba kwitabwaho, kubera ko bidahagije kwishingikiriza ku musingi washizweho kugira ngo isosiyete ikomeze kubaho neza, hagomba kubaho imbaraga zihoraho zo kubura abakiriya ba none no kubungabunga igikundiro. gishya.

Biremewe (a) gutanga inama ninama kubucuruzi buciriritse, buciriritse nubucuruzi bunini, mugihe byanditswe muburyo bwemewe ninama yubuyobozi (CFA ), kuva, kuva 1967, gutegura ibitekerezo, raporo, gahunda , imishinga, raporo, nibikorwa byumwuga. Usibye izi nshingano, umuntu ushinzwe kwamamaza niwe ushinzwe kwita ku kirango, agomba kumenyekanisha no gutangiza ibicuruzwa bishya, asobanura, urugero, ingamba, abarebwa intego, igiciro kizashyirwaho n'inzira zo kwamamaza.

Mu Giporutugali, kwamamaza byahinduwe mu kwamamaza. 

== Ibisobanuro ==
Dore bimwe mubisobanuro bifatwa nkibyingenzi:

* kuri gahunda, mumikoreshereze ya buri munsi, bisobanura "gucuruza", ariko kandi "kumenyekanisha". Ikubiyemo gahunda zose zo gutegura, gushushanya no gushyira mubikorwa ibikorwa bigamije guhaza ibyo umukiriya akeneye nigihe kizaza binyuze mubicuruzwa / serivisi bihari cyangwa bishya. Kwamamaza byerekana ibikenewe kandi bigatanga amahirwe.
* Hano haribisobanuro bimwe byavuzwe mubitabo byisi:
* Nibikorwa byubuyobozi hamwe nurutonde rwibikorwa birimo kurema, kuvugana no guha agaciro abakiriya no gucunga umubano wabakiriya muburyo bugirira akamaro umuryango nabafatanyabikorwa. (AMA - Ishyirahamwe ryamamaza Abanyamerika - Ibisobanuro 2005).
* nigikorwa, gushiraho ibigo nuburyo bwo kurema, kuvugana, gukwirakwiza no guhana amaturo afite agaciro kubakiriya, abakiriya, abafatanyabikorwa na societe muri rusange. (AMA - Ishyirahamwe ryamamaza Abanyamerika - Ibisobanuro 2008). 
* ni inzira mbonezamubano inyuramo abantu nitsinda ryabantu babona ibyo bakeneye kandi bashaka mugukora, gutanga no gucuruza kubuntu ibicuruzwa na serivisi byagaciro hamwe nabandi.
* ni ugutanga kunyurwa kwabakiriya muburyo bwinyungu (KOTLER na ARMSTRONG, 1999). 
* ni ibikorwa bya gahunda yumuryango wabantu bigamije gushaka no gukora kungurana ibitekerezo nibidukikije, bigamije inyungu zihariye.

* Kwamamaza nigikorwa cyagenewe gusobanukirwa no guhuza ibikenewe nabaguzi.
* ni urutonde rwibikorwa birimo ubuzima bwibicuruzwa, kuva igenamigambi ryibikorwa byayo kugeza igihe biguzwe nabaguzi (Inkoranyamagambo ya Michaelis).
* ni urutonde rwibikorwa nibikorwa bitanga iterambere, gutangiza no gushyigikira ibicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi kumasoko yabaguzi (Dicionário Novo Aurélio).
* urutonde rwibikorwa bikorwa nisosiyete irimo kugurisha ibicuruzwa, kuva igenamigambi ryibikorwa byayo kugeza igihe iguzwe nabaguzi (Inkoranyamagambo).
* niba byubahirijwe, ijambo rifata ibisobanuro byaryo: "isoko". Birashobora kuvugwa rero ko kwamamaza ari kwiga isoko. Nibikoresho byubuyobozi bifasha gukurikirana imigendekere no gushiraho amahirwe mashya yo gukoresha agamije kunezeza abakiriya no gusubiza intego zamafaranga nogucuruza ibicuruzwa cyangwa serivise (FRAGA, Robson, 2006).
* ni ugukangura, mubaguzi, ibyo bakandamijwe no kwerekana uburyo bwo kubihura binyuze mubicuruzwa na / cyangwa serivisi. (NÓBREGA, Moacir, 2008).
* nubushobozi bwo kumenya, binyuze mubushakashatsi bwubumenyi bwisoko, ibikenewe n'amahirwe y'ibicuruzwa na serivisi byakozwe kubantu runaka, kuzana inyungu zamafaranga na / cyangwa ubuyobozi kubakiriya binyuze mubikorwa byombi. (JAQUES, Leonardo, 2009).

* Kwamamaza uyumunsi bigomba kumvikana nkuburyo bwo gusobanukirwa umukiriya no guhaza ibyo bakeneye n'ibyifuzo byabo. Nibikorwa ibigo bitanga agaciro kubakiriya no kubaka umubano ukomeye nabo kugirango bafate agaciro kabo. (KOTLER & ARMSTRONG, 2007: 4)
* Kwamamaza ni inzira mbonezamubano inyuzamo abantu nitsinda ryabantu babona ibyo bakeneye kandi bashaka mugukora, gutanga no gucuruza kubuntu nibicuruzwa na serivisi byagaciro nabandi (KOTLER, 2000).
* Kotler (1998 p 27) agira ati: "Kwamamaza ni imibereho n'imiyoborere abantu ku giti cyabo n'amatsinda babona ibyo bakeneye kandi bashaka binyuze mu guhanga, gutanga no guhana ibicuruzwa bifite agaciro n'abandi". 
* Ati: “Guhana ni igikorwa cyo kubona ibicuruzwa umuntu yifuza mu gutanga ikintu runaka.” (Kotler, 1998 p 29) 
* <nowiki>'' Igikorwa cyibanze cyo kwamamaza ni ukumenya ibyo abaguzi bakeneye no guteza imbere ibicuruzwa bibahaza. Kubwibyo, uruhare rwo kwamamaza mumuryango ntirushobora kumenya ibyo abaguzi bakeneye nubushake bwabo, kumenya amasoko agamije umuryango ushobora gutanga neza, gutegura ibicuruzwa, serivisi, na gahunda bikwiranye no guhaza ayo masoko, ariko kandi bikahuriza hamwe. abitabira ishyirahamwe bagatekereza kandi bagakorera abaguzi. ''</nowiki> (MASO, 2010 p 3) 
* "Kwamamaza ni siyanse mbonezamubano igamije kuzamura intego z’inzego n’ubucuruzi binyuze muri gahunda n’amayeri, bishingiye ku bafatanyabikorwa bavugwa (buri wese abigizemo uruhare)." Ubumenyi mbonezamubano - burimo abantu, kubwibyo logique numubare ntibihagije, ubwenge busanzwe, ubushishozi no guhanga bigomba kwitabwaho buri gihe. Kuzamura intego - kongera ibishoboka, kurenga ibisubizo byateganijwe mumibanire y'umuntu ku giti cye (umwe kugeza kuri umwe), kugera kuri amplitude y'ibikorwa n'ibikorwa. Inzego - kunoza no / cyangwa kwagura ishusho. Ubucuruzi - kongera ibikorwa byimari. Gahunda ningamba - Ingamba nuburyo - Kwiga no gushyira mu bikorwa - Icyerekezo nigikorwa. Abafatanyabikorwa - Urunigi rw'agaciro. (Edson Zogbi 2014)

Kwamamaza, nk'uko Kotler abivuga (2011, p. 32), "ni inzira mbonezamubano n'imiyoborere abantu ku giti cyabo n'amatsinda babona ibyo bakeneye kandi bashaka binyuze mu guhanga, gutanga no guhana ibicuruzwa by'agaciro n'abandi".

Igitekerezo cya none cyo kwamamaza gikubiyemo kubaka umubano wigihe kirekire "win-win" aho abantu nitsinda babona ibyo bashaka kandi bakeneye. Kwamamaza byatangiye kugirango bikemure isoko, ariko ntabwo bigarukira kubicuruzwa. Irakoreshwa kandi cyane "kugurisha" ibitekerezo na gahunda zimibereho. Tekinike yo kwamamaza ikoreshwa muburyo bwose bwa politiki no mubice byinshi byubuzima.
